== Umwuga ==
Yatowe muri ''Best Actress /Most Promising Actres'' - Diaspora igihembo cya filime, message to  ''Brian'', aho yagaragaye mu bihembo bya Golden Icons Academy Movie Awards 2014 (GIAMA). <ref>http://nollysilverscreen.com/2014/08/12/the-giama-2014-nominees-are-here/</ref> Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere i Houston, muri Texas . <ref>http://goldenicons.com/a-message-to-brian-will-premiere-this-saturday-march-14th-2015-in-houston-texas-at-the-amc-theater/</ref> Yakinnye muri filime, ''Ndolor na Senateri'', yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 31 Mutarama 2016 i Houston, muri Texas. Filime yakozwe na Mbango Adambi ikayoborwa na Gordon Che yagaragayemo muri Nollywood ndetse nabakinnyi nka Mbango Adambi, Kelechi Eke, Frank Artus, Sunnyfield Okezie, Jasmine Roland, Eko Leonel, Ruth Taku, Bareh Mildred, Samson Tarh na Beatrice Nwana. <ref>https://www.victorymediapro.com/single-post/2016/2/1/Ndolor-and-the-Senator-Movie-Premiere-Houston-TX</ref>

Filime ye, ''Kiss of Death'', niyo filime yatangije mu birori bya CAMIFF 2017 ku ya 24 Mata. <ref>http://irepcamer.com/2017/04/26/is-camiff-the-answer-to-cameroons-struggling-film-industry/</ref> Yabaye umukinnyi wa mbere muri firime ya Kamerwood 2018, ''Tenacity'', anagaragaramo Libota McDonald, Mat Atugon, Vugah Samson na Eyo Eyo Michael. Iyi filime kandi yatsindiye igihembo ''cyiza cya Filime nziza'' muri CAMIFF Awards 2018. <ref>https://www.cameroon-tribune.cm/article.html/18718/fr.html/tenacity-africans-let-love</ref>
